this file describes the contents of the test directory.

the resources contains a tree Resources/STB400/UK/!EngMenu
which runs the tests described in the engineering menu design
specification 2501,834/DS.

the DENCemulat directory creates the testmod used in the tests
this emulates the macrovision module in calls to get TV standards
and channels this is simple but retained for completeness.

the setup directory contains the run files and the resource tags
file used in the tests, run this directory to set up the paths
this is best done from a web page on the STB.  Place this in the
public directory of the STB Boot image.  You will also have
to create an 'EngMenu_inst' directory in the public directory
the McCabe libraries construct a hard coded path to write its
output.